        Creates a list of datasets, which have the following properties:

        - dataset's owner is equals to the JPAUser parameter

        - dataset is visible

        - dataset was uploaded by the user (not by an experiment, which has run under user's name)

        Parameters:
        owner - the owner of the dataset
        offset - the position from which the elements are returned
        maxResultCount - maximum number of retrieved elements
        sortColumn - column upon which the result is sorted
        sortOrder - ascending or descending order of sorting
        Returns:
